<h4><a name="pseudo-tiling" id="pseudo-tiling">Pseudo-tiling</a></h4>
<div class="level4">

<p>
Aero-snap behavior is handled by the keyboard shortcuts 
&lt;super&gt;-&lt;alt&gt;-&lt;leftArrow&gt; and 
&lt;super&gt;-&lt;alt&gt;-&lt;rightArrow&gt;
where &lt;super&gt; usually corresponds to the windows key.
</p>

<p>
Windows can be incrementally resized with the shortcut &lt;super&gt;-&lt;arrow&gt;
</p>

<p>
By editing the rc.xml file, we can add additional keyboard shortcuts.
Add the following within the &lt;keyboard&gt; &lt;/keyboard&gt; section to be able to send a window to one of the four quadrants of the screen using 
&lt;super&gt;-&lt;num_pad_7&gt;, 
&lt;super&gt;-&lt;num_pad_9&gt;, 
&lt;super&gt;-&lt;num_pad_1&gt;, or
&lt;super&gt;-&lt;num_pad_3&gt;
</p>
<pre class="code">
    &lt;keybind key=&quot;W-KP_7&quot;&gt;
        &lt;action name=&quot;UnmaximizeFull&quot;/&gt; 
        &lt;action name=&quot;MoveResizeTo&quot;&gt;
            &lt;x&gt;0&lt;/x&gt;
            &lt;y&gt;0&lt;/y&gt;
            &lt;width&gt;50%&lt;/width&gt;
            &lt;height&gt;50%&lt;/height&gt;
        &lt;/action&gt; 
    &lt;/keybind&gt;
    &lt;keybind key=&quot;W-KP_9&quot;&gt;
        &lt;action name=&quot;UnmaximizeFull&quot;/&gt; 
        &lt;action name=&quot;MoveResizeTo&quot;&gt;
            &lt;x&gt;50%&lt;/x&gt;
            &lt;y&gt;0&lt;/y&gt;
            &lt;width&gt;50%&lt;/width&gt;
            &lt;height&gt;50%&lt;/height&gt;
        &lt;/action&gt; 
    &lt;/keybind&gt;
    &lt;keybind key=&quot;W-KP_1&quot;&gt;
        &lt;action name=&quot;UnmaximizeFull&quot;/&gt; 
        &lt;action name=&quot;MoveResizeTo&quot;&gt;
            &lt;x&gt;0&lt;/x&gt;
            &lt;y&gt;50%&lt;/y&gt;
            &lt;width&gt;50%&lt;/width&gt;
            &lt;height&gt;50%&lt;/height&gt;
        &lt;/action&gt; 
    &lt;/keybind&gt;
    &lt;keybind key=&quot;W-KP_3&quot;&gt;
        &lt;action name=&quot;UnmaximizeFull&quot;/&gt; 
        &lt;action name=&quot;MoveResizeTo&quot;&gt;
            &lt;x&gt;50%&lt;/x&gt;
            &lt;y&gt;50%&lt;/y&gt;
            &lt;width&gt;50%&lt;/width&gt;
            &lt;height&gt;50%&lt;/height&gt;
        &lt;/action&gt; 
    &lt;/keybind&gt;
</pre>

</div>

    <!-- end rendered wiki content -->
    <div class="clearer"></div>
